text: Johan Fredrik Håkansson (born August 2, 1975) is a male Swedish international table tennis player. He won a gold medal at the 2000 World Team Table Tennis Championships in the men's team and the following year he won a bronze medal at the 2001 World Table Tennis Championships in the men's teams. He also competed in the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==See also== * List of table tennis players * List of World Table Tennis Championships medalists ==References== ==External links== * Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of Sweden Category:Table tennis players at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists
